    "description": "<strong>天空 的幸存者</strong>是一款竞技场射击游戏roguelite。从各种技能中选择，解锁独特的角色和武器。建造 &quot;通向天堂的阶梯&quot;--一座天空之塔，每一层都会给你的角色带来独特的奖励。创建你自己的超强建筑，在面对成群的怪物时生存下来!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/92ae25a9c4192eaf45d91ad9ccbd7cf8.webp?t=1701195497\" width=599 height=58 /></span><br>超过100种不同的技能将帮助你在每次运行时创建一个独特的构建。你可以成为一个元素法师，一个武器大师，或者召唤魔法书来摧毁你的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/8403857be41e650ed274cb1a50008f55.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/b43a8f6c45e5f911ce8be0737cb934a1.webp?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=53 /></span><br>每种武器都有自己的独特玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/410b3bb072df82ebb94f2e0ea8a2978d.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/aaeb9b534b0f310b3e607f9b0acb9f3d.avif?t=1701195497\" width=574 height=93 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bullet Hell — 经典的 &quot;roguelike&quot;。怪物和它们的弹丸的速度增加。你和怪物受到的伤害更大。<br></li><li>Deckbuilder — 妖怪的数量和获得的经验都会增加。<br></li><li>Standard Mode — 完美的第一次.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/210a9f1688cac7d7dd61a1bf540a3701.webp?t=1701195497\" width=620 height=61 /></span><br>建造一个 &quot;通向天堂的楼梯&quot;--授予你的角色独特的永久奖励或强大的临时BUFF的楼层。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.poster.avif?t=1701195497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.webm?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/337c4dad6cfdc73823c0c6929d601478.mp4?t=1701195497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331710/extras/24e12c0f13e0e0b690b6a660927733a5.webp?t=1701195497\" width=134 height=37 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏手柄和PC的自动瞄准模式</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过100种不同的技能可供选择。</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;天梯&quot;--每层楼都有自己独特的奖金。</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的武器，完全改变了你的游戏风格。</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的角色： 黑暗物质法师、躲避者、轰炸机。</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种游戏模式让你可以根据自己的喜好选择玩法。</h2></li></ul>",
